---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import tmc from "@/assets/images/tmc.jpeg"
---

<section class="pb-10 pt-24 md:py-24 text-[#1A30FF]">
	<div class="max-w-[1480px] mx-auto px-8 md:px-10">
		<div class="mb-10">
			<h2
				class="text-4xl text-balance md:text-5xl font-condensed font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-4 max-w-prose">
				Hello! My name is Troy.
			</h2>
			<p class="prose text-[#1A30FF]">I like to write code.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20">
			<div class="relative aspect-square">
				<Image
					class="absolute w-full h-full object-cover"
					src={tmc}
					alt="Troy Ciesco"
				/>
				<div class="bg-[#1a31ff90] absolute w-full h-full top-2 right-2 -z-[1]">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div class="prose text-[#1A30FF]">
					<div class="font-bold">10+ Years of Full Stack Development</div> I was
					working for a municipality in 2014 when they asked for some help updating
					their website, and since then I've been hooked. About 65% of the time I'm
					doing frontend development with React or Vue. The rest of the time is backend
					development with TypeScript or Python.
				</div>
				<hr class="prose text-[#1a31ff90]" />
				<div class="prose text-[#1A30FF]">
					<div class="font-bold">Diverse Work Experience</div> I've worked in a bunch
					of environments: startups/scaleups (Gemini), FAANG-ish (Hulu), agencies,
					and freelance. I also spent six years in the US Army Reserve.
				</div>
				<hr class="prose text-[#1a31ff90]" />
				<div class="prose text-[#1A30FF]">
					<div class="font-bold">Career Highlights (so far!)</div>
					<ul
						class="mb-8 list-disc text-[#1A30FF] prose marker:text-[#1a31ff90]">
						<li class="mb-2">
							Building marketing pages and purchase logic for the
							<a
								class="font-bold underline decoration-double text-[#1A30FF]"
								href="https://niftygateway.com/collections/pakmerge"
								>$91m Pak NFT sale</a
							>, the (as of June 2022) largest NFT sale and largest ever art
							sale by a living creator
						</li>
						<li class="mb-2">
							Building a site associated with a Super Bowl commerical that
							received 1m+ page views and 250k+ signups
						</li>
						<li class="mb-2">
							Leading a team of four to overhaul a Wordpress website for a
							$10m/yr company that provides
							<a
								class="font-bold underline decoration-double text-[#1A30FF]"
								href="https://nicabm.com"
								>training for mental health professionals</a
							>
						</li>
						<li class="mb-2">
							<a
								class="font-bold underline decoration-double text-[#1A30FF]"
								href="https://medium.com/@tmciesco/the-burrito-method-of-task-estimation-973df97509bb">
								Writing about
							</a> how a scrum team can think about estimating tasks. ðŸŒ¯
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
